Unit Test 1: LSASS Memory Dump
```python
import unittest
from lsass_utils import lsass_memory_dump

class TestLSASSMemoryDump(unittest.TestCase):

    def test_lsass_memory_dump(self):
        result = lsass_memory_dump()
        self.assertIsNotNone(result)
        self.assertEqual(result[-4:], ".bin")

if __name__ == '__main__':
    unittest.main()
```
